    {
        "url": "/quotes/paolo_bacigalupi_715833",
        "quote": "Sometimes when we label something dystopian fiction, I feel like we're trying very hard not to use the words 'science fiction,' because science fiction has those horrible connotations of rocket ships and bodacious babes.",
