    {
        "url": "/quotes/paolo_bacigalupi_715836",
        "quote": "When we live the 21st-century good life, almost every aspect of it is predicated on not looking at the implications of what we're up to. Happiness at this point has a lot to do with not looking, so you don't feel complicit in some vast and awful enterprise.",
